	<Row id="1022" name="『打听道路』" chapter="1" type="1" triggerLevel="1" preTask="1021" timeLimit="0" abandomTimeLimit="0" rewardsStr="152_1_1,5_0_1800" describe="" acceptNpc="10117" initTarget="对话：{W 10002 10117 0 0 0|猪八戒}" unfinishedTarget="向{W 10002 10101 0 0 0|善财童子}打听通往花果山的道路。" submitNpc="10101" finishedTarget="向{W 10002 10101 0 0 0|善财童子}打听通往花果山的道路。" state="1" publishWord="" publishReply="" publishReward="" unfinishWord="" unfinishReply="" unfinishReward="" submitWord="你要去花果山呀！花果山之路就在南门以东。只可惜我要接引众仙友，不能陪你同去。你可去南门寻唐大仙，他自会指引你如何消灭路上荆棘。" submitReply="" submitReward="1" failedWord="" failedReply="" failedReward="" />
	<Row id="1023" name="『仙人指路』" chapter="1" type="1" triggerLevel="1" preTask="1022" timeLimit="0" abandomTimeLimit="0" rewardsStr="10007_1_1,10017_1_1,10027_1_1,10037_1_1,5_0_2000" describe="" acceptNpc="10101" initTarget="对话：{W 10002 10101 0 0 0|善财童子}" unfinishedTarget="南门有个{W 10002 10115 0 0 0|唐大仙}，自会仙人指路。" submitNpc="10115" finishedTarget="南门有个{W 10002 10115 0 0 0|唐大仙}，自会仙人指路。" state="1" publishWord="" publishReply="" publishReward="" unfinishWord="" unfinishReply="" unfinishReward="" submitWord="你来得正好，我和我那孪生弟弟唐半仙的推理相同，此劫八成和那取经人有关。只不过通往花果山之路被一群菩提树精堵塞了，还得清理。" submitReply="" submitReward="1" failedWord="" failedReply="" failedReward="" />
	<Row id="1024" name="『菩提树精』" chapter="1" type="1" triggerLevel="1" preTask="1023" timeLimit="0" abandomTimeLimit="0" rewardsStr="128_1_1,5_0_2400" describe="" acceptNpc="10115" initTarget="对话：{W 10002 10115 0 0 0|唐大仙}" unfinishedTarget="清理花果山之路，击杀：{W 10002 20107 0 0 0|菩提树精}（[:npcnum]/10）" submitNpc="10103" finishedTarget="质问栽下菩提树的{W 10002 10103 0 0 0|菩提老祖}。" state="1" publishWord="" publishReply="" publishReward="" unfinishWord="" unfinishReply="" unfinishReward="" submitWord="说来惭愧！这些菩提树乃贫道亲手所植，未曾想到竟成这副模样。这一切，都是那地府跳出的索命判官乱判生死错划物种所致，看你的了！" submitReply="" submitReward="1" failedWord="" failedReply="" failedReward="" />
	<Row id="1025" name="『索命判官』" chapter="1" type="1" triggerLevel="1" preTask="1024" timeLimit="0" abandomTimeLimit="0" rewardsStr="10010_1_1,10020_1_1,10030_1_1,10040_1_1,5_0_3200" describe="" acceptNpc="10103" initTarget="对话：{W 10002 10103 0 0 0|菩提老祖}" unfinishedTarget="前往黄泉路，击杀{W 10002 20110 0 0 0|索命判官}（[:npcnum]/1）" submitNpc="10103" finishedTarget="成功击杀索命判官，向{W 10002 10103 0 0 0|菩提老祖}汇报。" state="1" publishWord="" publishReply="" publishReward="" unfinishWord="" unfinishReply="" unfinishReward="" submitWord="看来我没有看错你天资聪慧的你！虽然天下都在怀疑这千魔之血与孙悟空有关，然而我并不信。去花果山调查一番，务必替孙悟空洗刷冤屈。" submitReply="" submitReward="1" failedWord="" failedReply="" failedReward="" />
	<Row id="1026" name="『花果山』" chapter="2" type="1" triggerLevel="1" preTask="1025" timeLimit="0" abandomTimeLimit="0" rewardsStr="118_1_10,5_0_1900" describe="" acceptNpc="10103" initTarget="对话：{W 10002 10103 0 0 0|菩提老祖}" unfinishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10117 0 0 0|傲来将军}" submitNpc="10115" finishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10117 0 0 0|傲来将军}" state="1" publishWord="" publishReply="" publishReward="" unfinishWord="" unfinishReply="" unfinishReward="" submitWord="什么？你来调查孙悟空和千魔之血？呵呵，正好，此地的确有猴王作怪，我奉傲来国王之命前来镇压，先去除那猴王布下的瞌睡虫吧！" submitReply="" submitReward="1" failedWord="" failedReply="" failedReward="" />
	<Row id="1027" name="『瞌睡虫』" chapter="2" type="1" triggerLevel="1" preTask="1026" timeLimit="0" abandomTimeLimit="0" rewardsStr="5_0_1901" describe="" acceptNpc="10115" initTarget="对话：{W 10002 10115 0 0 0|傲来将军}" unfinishedTarget="击杀：{W 10002 20110 0 0 0|瞌睡虫}（[:npcnum]/4）" submitNpc="10116" finishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10116 0 0 0|白眉老猿}" state="1" publishWord="" publishReply="" publishReward="" unfinishWord="" unfinishReply="" unfinishReward="" submitWord="大梦谁先觉，平生我自知。要不是你除了瞌睡虫，我真不知道要睡到何时。看来在我睡着之后这里发生了很多事，怎会凭空多出一些竹妖来？" submitReply="" submitReward="1" failedWord="" failedReply="" failedReward="" />
	<Row id="1028" name="『清理竹妖』" chapter="2" type="1" triggerLevel="1" preTask="1027" timeLimit="0" abandomTimeLimit="0" rewardsStr="10006_1_1,10016_1_1,10026_1_1,10036_1_1,5_0_1902" describe="" acceptNpc="10116" initTarget="对话：{W 10002 10116 0 0 0|白眉老猿}" unfinishedTarget="击杀：{W 10002 20111 0 0 0|竹妖}（[:npcnum]/4）" submitNpc="10117" finishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10117 0 0 0|镇元大仙}" state="1" publishWord="" publishReply="" publishReward="" unfinishWord="" unfinishReply="" unfinishReward="" submitWord="你是神仙，得让我三分；你是妖怪，得敬我三分。你若问我此地为何变成这般光景，你觉得我会告诉一个蝼蚁吗？给你点甜头，速速离开吧！" submitReply="" submitReward="1" failedWord="" failedReply="" failedReward="" />
	<Row id="1029" name="『查明风物』" chapter="2" type="1" triggerLevel="1" preTask="1028" timeLimit="0" abandomTimeLimit="0" rewardsStr="5_0_1903" describe="" acceptNpc="10117" initTarget="对话：{W 10002 10117 0 0 0|镇元大仙}" unfinishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10118 0 0 0|花果山土地}" submitNpc="10118" finishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10118 0 0 0|花果山土地}" state="1" publishWord="" publishReply="" publishReward="" unfinishWord="" unfinishReply="" unfinishReward="" submitWord="嘘~休要喧哗！千万别吵醒了那魔悟空！他从五庄观盗来了人参果，然而果子水土不服，在此产生异变。唉！个中缘由，只有白眉老猿最清楚。" submitReply="" submitReward="1" failedWord="" failedReply="" failedReward="" />
	<Row id="1030" name="『幻象』" chapter="2" type="1" triggerLevel="1" preTask="1029" timeLimit="0" abandomTimeLimit="0" rewardsStr="102_1_99,5_0_1904" describe="" acceptNpc="10118" initTarget="对话：{W 10002 10118 0 0 0|花果山土地}" unfinishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10116 0 0 0|白眉老猿}" submitNpc="10116" finishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10116 0 0 0|白眉老猿}" state="1" publishWord="" publishReply="" publishReward="" unfinishWord="" unfinishReply="" unfinishReward="" submitWord="你也看到了，那恶怪不仅拿我们花果山作人参果的实验基地，而且利用幻象使我们猴群分崩离析。老朋友哪吒在湖心亭已经发现了幻象的来源。" submitReply="" submitReward="1" failedWord="" failedReply="" failedReward="" />
	<Row id="1031" name="『假象妄念』" chapter="2" type="1" triggerLevel="1" preTask="1030" timeLimit="0" abandomTimeLimit="0" rewardsStr="5_0_1905" describe="" acceptNpc="10116" initTarget="对话：{W 10002 10116 0 0 0|白眉老猿}" unfinishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10104 0 0 0|哪吒}" submitNpc="10104" finishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10104 0 0 0|哪吒}" state="1" publishWord="" publishReply="" publishReward="" unfinishWord="" unfinishReply="" unfinishReward="" submitWord="猴群之所以被蛊惑心智，乃是相信水中捞月的幻象能带来希望，然而幻象始终是幻象，希望也只是假象。我做了一轮可被捞起的月亮，希望你让他们警醒。" submitReply="" submitReward="1" failedWord="" failedReply="" failedReward="" />
	<Row id="1032" name="『水中捞月』" chapter="2" type="1" triggerLevel="1" preTask="1031" timeLimit="0" abandomTimeLimit="0" rewardsStr="5_0_1906" describe="" acceptNpc="10104" initTarget="对话：{W 10002 10104 0 0 0|哪吒}" unfinishedTarget="采集：{W 10002 20112 0 0 0|井中月}" submitNpc="10104" finishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10104 0 0 0|哪吒}" state="1" publishWord="" publishReply="" publishReward="" unfinishWord="" unfinishReply="" unfinishReward="" submitWord="做得不错，猴群们捞了几百年的月亮竟然被你轻松捞起，你终结了他们的幻象。现在，他们都跟失心疯般癫狂了，快去用你的武器使他们清醒吧！" submitReply="" submitReward="1" failedWord="" failedReply="" failedReward="" />
	<Row id="1033" name="『魔猿之灾』" chapter="2" type="1" triggerLevel="1" preTask="1032" timeLimit="0" abandomTimeLimit="0" rewardsStr="5_0_1907" describe="" acceptNpc="10104" initTarget="对话：{W 10002 10104 0 0 0|哪吒}" unfinishedTarget="击杀：{W 10002 20113 0 0 0|魔猿}（[:npcnum]/4）" submitNpc="10115" finishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10115 0 0 0|傲来将军}" state="1" publishWord="" publishReply="" publishReward="" unfinishWord="" unfinishReply="" unfinishReward="" submitWord="看得出来，你很热心。如今魔猿即除，你当更加深入一点铲除魔石怪。那些魔石怪质地皆来自五庄观，不尽快铲除，这里迟早变成另一座万寿山。" submitReply="" submitReward="1" failedWord="" failedReply="" failedReward="" />
	<Row id="1034" name="『巨力魔石』" chapter="2" type="1" triggerLevel="1" preTask="1033" timeLimit="0" abandomTimeLimit="0" rewardsStr="10007_1_1,10017_1_1,10027_1_1,10037_1_1,,5_0_1908" describe="" acceptNpc="10115" initTarget="对话：{W 10002 10115 0 0 0|傲来将军}" unfinishedTarget="击杀：{W 10002 20114 0 0 0|魔石怪}（[:npcnum]/4）" submitNpc="10115" finishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10115 0 0 0|傲来将军}" state="1" publishWord="" publishReply="" publishReward="" unfinishWord="" unfinishReply="" unfinishReward="" submitWord="看到那些无花果妖了么？当第一粒人参果核在花果山生根之后，他们便也同时孕育了。就是因为他们的存在，花果山如今才无花无果。" submitReply="" submitReward="1" failedWord="" failedReply="" failedReward="" />
	<Row id="1035" name="『无花果』" chapter="2" type="1" triggerLevel="1" preTask="1034" timeLimit="0" abandomTimeLimit="0" rewardsStr="118_1_10,5_0_1909" describe="" acceptNpc="10115" initTarget="对话：{W 10002 10115 0 0 0傲来将军}" unfinishedTarget="击杀：{W 10002 20115 0 0 0|无花果}（[:npcnum]/4）" submitNpc="10117" finishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10117 0 0 0|镇元大仙}" state="1" publishWord="" publishReply="" publishReward="" unfinishWord="" unfinishReply="" unfinishReward="" submitWord="如你所见，花果山如今成为这副光景，作为地仙之首的我深感难辞其咎。现在想来，假如当日我看管好那两个顽劣之徒的话，也许不会这么糟。" submitReply="" submitReward="1" failedWord="" failedReply="" failedReward="" />
	<Row id="1036" name="『魔祭妖童』" chapter="2" type="1" triggerLevel="1" preTask="1035" timeLimit="0" abandomTimeLimit="0" rewardsStr="5_0_1910" describe="" acceptNpc="10117" initTarget="对话：{W 10002 10117 0 0 0|镇元大仙}" unfinishedTarget="击杀：{W 10002 20116 0 0 0|妖童}（[:npcnum]/4）" submitNpc="10118" finishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10118 0 0 0|花果山土地}" state="1" publishWord="" publishReply="" publishReward="" unfinishWord="" unfinishReply="" unfinishReward="" submitWord="你如此辛苦奔波，然而却不知此地魔物根源皆来自于六道轮回。那白眉老猿已调查出进入六道轮回的方法，快去助他清剿吧！" submitReply="" submitReward="1" failedWord="" failedReply="" failedReward="" />
	<Row id="1037" name="『引路地府』" chapter="2" type="1" triggerLevel="1" preTask="1036" timeLimit="0" abandomTimeLimit="0" rewardsStr="111_1_1,112_1_1,5_0_1911" describe="" acceptNpc="10118" initTarget="对话：{W 10002 10118 0 0 0|花果山土地}" unfinishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10116 0 0 0|白眉老猿}" submitNpc="10116" finishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10116 0 0 0|白眉老猿}" state="1" publishWord="" publishReply="" publishReward="" unfinishWord="" unfinishReply="" unfinishReward="" submitWord="想必那个老土地已经告诉你了，进入六道轮回需要一张地府引路府，而合成地府引路符需要一道鬼画符和一张生死残页，快去合成吧！" submitReply="" submitReward="1" failedWord="" failedReply="" failedReward="" />
	<Row id="1038" name="『大闹地府』" chapter="2" type="1" triggerLevel="1" preTask="1037" timeLimit="0" abandomTimeLimit="0" rewardsStr="10008_1_1,10018_1_1,10028_1_1,10038_1_1,,5_0_1912" describe="" acceptNpc="10116" initTarget="对话：{W 10002 10116 0 0 0|白眉老猿}" unfinishedTarget="引导合成，进入大闹地府" submitNpc="10116" finishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10116 0 0 0|白眉老猿}" state="0" publishWord="" publishReply="" publishReward="" unfinishWord="" unfinishReply="" unfinishReward="" submitWord="看来你也的确有些本事，大闹地府一场，暂时阻止了六道轮回上的邪魔向花果山入侵。今后你可以时常去地府一游，将那些魔物尽收于掌下！快去杀鬼童子吧！" submitReply="" submitReward="1" failedWord="" failedReply="" failedReward="" />
	<Row id="1039" name="『除魔鬼童』" chapter="2" type="1" triggerLevel="1" preTask="1038" timeLimit="0" abandomTimeLimit="0" rewardsStr="5_0_1913" describe="" acceptNpc="10116" initTarget="对话：{W 10002 10116 0 0 0|白眉老猿}" unfinishedTarget="击杀：{W 10002 20117 0 0 0|鬼童子}（[:npcnum]/5）" submitNpc="10117" finishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10117 0 0 0|镇元大仙}" state="1" publishWord="" publishReply="" publishReward="" unfinishWord="" unfinishReply="" unfinishReward="" submitWord="这些鬼童子实则是明月那顽劣徒儿的恶怨所化，你做得很好。人参果变异的地点就在鬼童子的东边，去消灭那些惨不忍睹的妖果娃娃吧。" submitReply="" submitReward="1" failedWord="" failedReply="" failedReward="" />
	<Row id="1040" name="『妖果娃娃』" chapter="2" type="1" triggerLevel="1" preTask="1039" timeLimit="0" abandomTimeLimit="0" rewardsStr="5_0_1914" describe="" acceptNpc="10117" initTarget="对话：{W 10002 10117 0 0 0|镇元大仙}" unfinishedTarget="击杀：{W 10002 20118 0 0 0|妖果娃娃}（[:npcnum]/5）" submitNpc="10115" finishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10115 0 0 0|傲来将军}" state="1" publishWord="" publishReply="" publishReward="" unfinishWord="" unfinishReply="" unfinishReward="" submitWord="变异的人参果已经清除，那藏在水帘洞的魔悟空早已按捺不住了，他的怒吼我在这里也能隐隐听到。请务必穿上最好的装备带上最好的补给去给他迎头痛击！" submitReply="" submitReward="1" failedWord="" failedReply="" failedReward="" />
	<Row id="1041" name="『水帘降魔』" chapter="2" type="1" triggerLevel="1" preTask="1040" timeLimit="0" abandomTimeLimit="0" rewardsStr="5_0_1915" describe="" acceptNpc="10115" initTarget="对话：{W 10002 10115 0 0 0|傲来将军}" unfinishedTarget="击杀：{W 10002 20119 0 0 0|魔悟空}（[:npcnum]/1）" submitNpc="10115" finishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10115 0 0 0|傲来将军}" state="1" publishWord="" publishReply="" publishReward="" unfinishWord="" unfinishReply="" unfinishReward="" submitWord="不错！如此一来，花果山即可恢复往日祥和了。请你务必立刻赶往长安，告知菩提，那洞中的魔物并非真正的孙悟空，孙行者的嫌疑可暂时洗脱了。" submitReply="" submitReward="1" failedWord="" failedReply="" failedReward="" />
	<Row id="1042" name="『回城通报』" chapter="2" type="1" triggerLevel="1" preTask="1041" timeLimit="0" abandomTimeLimit="0" rewardsStr="5_0_1916" describe="" acceptNpc="10115" initTarget="对话：{W 10002 10115 0 0 0|傲来将军}" unfinishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10103 0 0 0|菩提老祖}" submitNpc="10103" finishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10103 0 0 0|菩提老祖}" state="1" publishWord="" publishReply="" publishReward="" unfinishWord="" unfinishReply="" unfinishReward="" submitWord="我就知道那猢狲断然不会做出这种事来。这件事最好让那杨戬知道，否则他又该去到处传孙悟空的坏话了。" submitReply="" submitReward="1" failedWord="" failedReply="" failedReward="" />
	<Row id="1043" name="『神将勿扰』" chapter="2" type="1" triggerLevel="1" preTask="1042" timeLimit="0" abandomTimeLimit="0" rewardsStr="5_0_1917" describe="" acceptNpc="10103" initTarget="对话：{W 10002 10103 0 0 0|菩提老祖}" unfinishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10108 0 0 0|杨戬}" submitNpc="10108" finishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10108 0 0 0|杨戬}" state="1" publishWord="" publishReply="" publishReward="" unfinishWord="" unfinishReply="" unfinishReward="" submitWord="原来是这样，难得你亲自到花果山去验证那戾气的真身。如此看来，这千魔之血并非如此简单，需联合三界的共同力量，你去找灵妖掌门商议此事吧！" submitReply="" submitReward="1" failedWord="" failedReply="" failedReward="" />
	<Row id="1044" name="『联合灵妖』" chapter="2" type="1" triggerLevel="1" preTask="1043" timeLimit="0" abandomTimeLimit="0" rewardsStr="5_0_1918" describe="" acceptNpc="10108" initTarget="对话：{W 10002 10108 0 0 0|杨戬}" unfinishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10109 0 0 0|天狐}" submitNpc="10109" finishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10109 0 0 0|天狐}" state="1" publishWord="" publishReply="" publishReward="" unfinishWord="" unfinishReply="" unfinishReward="" submitWord="我们灵妖界向来与世无争，既然需要三界联合，我们自当义不容辞。鉴于你如此精彩的表现，天仙掌门给你略备了一些薄礼，快去领取吧！" submitReply="" submitReward="1" failedWord="" failedReply="" failedReward="" />
	<Row id="1045" name="『天仙薄礼』" chapter="2" type="1" triggerLevel="1" preTask="1044" timeLimit="0" abandomTimeLimit="0" rewardsStr="118_1,10,5_0_1919" describe="" acceptNpc="10109" initTarget="对话：{W 10002 10109 0 0 0|天狐}" unfinishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10110 0 0 0|乾达婆}" submitNpc="10110" finishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10110 0 0 0|乾达婆}" state="1" publishWord="" publishReply="" publishReward="" unfinishWord="" unfinishReply="" unfinishReward="" submitWord="你总算来了，我已经等你好久。在你排除了花果山的嫌疑之后，修罗王也通过六道轮回的千魔之血调查出新的线索，快去一探究竟吧！" submitReply="" submitReward="1" failedWord="" failedReply="" failedReward="" />
	<Row id="1046" name="『修罗探察』" chapter="2" type="1" triggerLevel="1" preTask="1045" timeLimit="0" abandomTimeLimit="0" rewardsStr="5_0_1920" describe="" acceptNpc="10110" initTarget="对话：{W 10002 10110 0 0 0|乾达婆}" unfinishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10106 0 0 0|修罗王}" submitNpc="10106" finishedTarget="对话：{W 10002 10106 0 0 0|修罗王}" state="1" publishWord="" publishReply="" publishReward="" unfinishWord="" unfinishReply="" unfinishReward="" submitWord="那滴下千魔之血的人虽说不是孙悟空，然而却也是在取经人中无疑。因为那集齐千魔之血的容器正是沙僧当年修复好的琉璃盏。" submitReply="（剧情交待流沙河背景以及去路）" submitReward="1" failedWord="" failedReply="" failedReward="" />
